  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490590/extras/9866ea0a9eb0c97c0c117f58d7f6d8ea.poster.avif?t=1748480195\" width=600 height=169 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490590/extras/9866ea0a9eb0c97c0c117f58d7f6d8ea.webm?t=1748480195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Are you reading this? Hi! My name is <strong>Eva</strong>. I'm the main protagonist of the game you're looking at. Yes, this little platformer game is about <strong>me</strong>... About me AND dimensional travel! Do you want to know more?<br><br>Okay, well... I am a <i>(mostly)</i> peaceful creature living between different worlds. Sleeping is usually all I do, but right now, something evil is happening to said worlds, and I want it to stop. That's where I need you, for your ability to see in 2D... <i><strong>There's no time to explain!!!1</strong></i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DIMENSIONAL TRAVEL</h2>Play the game in multiple dimensions <strong>simultaneously</strong>, traveling through them at will!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490590/extras/fc819f9d60ceefb8b26b8785cfe11005.poster.avif?t=1748480195\" width=600 height=169 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490590/extras/fc819f9d60ceefb8b26b8785cfe11005.webm?t=1748480195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NOT JUST DECORATIONS</h2>All worlds are <strong>truly</strong> different! One might not let you breathe, while the other will allow you to fly!..<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490590/extras/2c552635d2537a210118534cc7e4da58.poster.avif?t=1748480195\" width=600 height=169 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490590/extras/2c552635d2537a210118534cc7e4da58.webm?t=1748480195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DYNAMIC LEVELS</h2>Each level <strong>changes</strong> whenever you fail! Say \"yes!\" to an ever-fresh experience!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490590/extras/0fe027586814e25dc5fca8d481432460.poster.avif?t=1748480195\" width=600 height=169 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490590/extras/0fe027586814e25dc5fca8d481432460.webm?t=1748480195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FREEDOM OF MOVEMENT</h2>Make <strong>your</strong> way! And if it doesn't work, make another one.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490590/extras/7393edbd6cbcae1821c076eac8a5e8cd.poster.avif?t=1748480195\" width=600 height=169 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490590/extras/7393edbd6cbcae1821c076eac8a5e8cd.webm?t=1748480195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >YOUR CHARISMATIC COMPANION</h2>The <strong>best</strong> playable character in the history of gaming <i>(according to herself)</i> will never leave you alone! EVER. <i>(guys, we should rewrite this - it sounds like a threat)</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490590/extras/ebf60ddf62a81330cb3f0ec1ee64db82.poster.avif?t=1748480195\" width=600 height=169 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490590/extras/ebf60ddf62a81330cb3f0ec1ee64db82.webm?t=1748480195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490590/extras/9866ea0a9eb0c97c0c117f58d7f6d8ea.poster.avif?t=1748480195\" width=600 height=169 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490590/extras/9866ea0a9eb0c97c0c117f58d7f6d8ea.webm?t=1748480195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Are you reading this? Hi! My name is <strong>Eva</strong>. I'm the main protagonist of the game you're looking at. Yes, this little platformer game is about <strong>me</strong>... About me AND dimensional travel! Do you want to know more?<br><br>Okay, well... I am a <i>(mostly)</i> peaceful creature living between different worlds. Sleeping is usually all I do, but right now, something evil is happening to said worlds, and I want it to stop. That's where I need you, for your ability to see in 2D... <i><strong>There's no time to explain!!!1</strong></i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DIMENSIONAL TRAVEL</h2>Play the game in multiple dimensions <strong>simultaneously</strong>, traveling through them at will!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490590/extras/fc819f9d60ceefb8b26b8785cfe11005.poster.avif?t=1748480195\" width=600 height=169 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490590/extras/fc819f9d60ceefb8b26b8785cfe11005.webm?t=1748480195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NOT JUST DECORATIONS</h2>All worlds are <strong>truly</strong> different! One might not let you breathe, while the other will allow you to fly!..<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490590/extras/2c552635d2537a210118534cc7e4da58.poster.avif?t=1748480195\" width=600 height=169 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490590/extras/2c552635d2537a210118534cc7e4da58.webm?t=1748480195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DYNAMIC LEVELS</h2>Each level <strong>changes</strong> whenever you fail! Say \"yes!\" to an ever-fresh experience!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490590/extras/0fe027586814e25dc5fca8d481432460.poster.avif?t=1748480195\" width=600 height=169 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490590/extras/0fe027586814e25dc5fca8d481432460.webm?t=1748480195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FREEDOM OF MOVEMENT</h2>Make <strong>your</strong> way! And if it doesn't work, make another one.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490590/extras/7393edbd6cbcae1821c076eac8a5e8cd.poster.avif?t=1748480195\" width=600 height=169 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490590/extras/7393edbd6cbcae1821c076eac8a5e8cd.webm?t=1748480195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >YOUR CHARISMATIC COMPANION</h2>The <strong>best</strong> playable character in the history of gaming <i>(according to herself)</i> will never leave you alone! EVER. <i>(guys, we should rewrite this - it sounds like a threat)</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps